  <brief_title>Transcystic Versus Transanastomotic Tube Drainage in Right Lobe LDLT</brief_title>
  <official_title>Transcystic Versus Transanastomotic Biliary Drainage Tubes in Living Donor Liver Transplantation. A Prospective Randomized Trial.</official_title>
